{"id":12297,"date":"2024-07-15T17:36:43","date_gmt":"2024-07-15T22:36:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co\/?page_id=12297"},"modified":"2024-08-08T11:20:41","modified_gmt":"2024-08-08T16:20:41","slug":"admissions-step-by-step","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co\/admissions-step-by-step\/","title":{"rendered":"Admissions Step by Step"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"12297\" class=\"elementor elementor-12297\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-567b605 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-height-min-height hero-banner-internal-page elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-items-middle ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"567b605\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-65257c9 ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"65257c9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b005d30 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b005d30\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Apply<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-eb6c7f5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"eb6c7f5\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1fe8384 ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"1fe8384\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3287d8a elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"3287d8a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-968f34a h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"968f34a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">INSTRUCTIONS TO APPLY\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dc97cb4 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dc97cb4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">APPLICATION FORM Complete the <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/cgb-online.net\/crm\/custom\/admisiones\/registroinicial.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Application Form<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and upload the corresponding <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/presentation\/d\/16lGmEgtIK5ZnRR0UHTK9OFlyciiuQs6DrBHsodkSL3Y\/edit#slide=id.p\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">documents. <\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(please provide English translations where applicable). <\/span><br \/><a href=\"https:\/\/cgb-online.net\/crm\/custom\/admisiones\/registroinicial.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/cgb-online.net\/crm\/custom\/admisiones\/registroinicial.php<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">REFERENCES FROM TEACHERS: Please provide the email addresses of your children\u2019s current teachers, counselor, or section coordinators on the application form. The system automatically sends a \u201cConfidential Student Reference Form\u201d to the provided email addresses. We need a minimum of two forms per student, preferably three.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ADMISSION FEE. Once you complete the application form, we will send instructions for paying the 300,000 COP application fee. We will then contact you to schedule the admissions appointment, which is usually held on Fridays between 8:30 a.m. and 12:00 midday (Colombian time).<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">STUDENT INTERVIEWS. Applicants will participate in different interviews\/observations led by our specialists. Each interview lasts approximately 30 minutes, and each student will have three interviews.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PARENTS INTERVIEW Parents will have a 30-minute interview with our counsellor, usually scheduled on the same day. Both parents\/legal guardians need to attend this interview.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">OBSERVATION PRESCHOOL STUDENTS Our specialists will observe applicants applying to preschool (Nursery, Reception, Year 1, and Year 2) to check their motor skills, language skills, and independence.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ENTRY TESTS Students applying for Year 3 up to Year 13 must complete two tests: the <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.idat.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">iDAT<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and a writing test.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ONLINE OR ON SITE. Students in Colombia must come to the school on the admissions appointment day from 8:30 a.m. to 12:00 midday. If they are applying from abroad, the whole process can be done online.\u00a0<\/span><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-aef2853 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"aef2853\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b0d3a5d animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"b0d3a5d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3501fe5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"3501fe5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7eef99f animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"7eef99f\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6926b24 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"6926b24\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fbb555d h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fbb555d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Additional instructions for students applying online. <\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c2dfb5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"3c2dfb5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e532c41 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e532c41\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The tests and interviews can be taken from home, and one of the parents can act as the &#8220;proctor.&#8221;\u00a0<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order to receive the test instructions, the proctor must complete the following <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/form.jotform.com\/200773877013658\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Proctor Agreement<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and the parents must complete the <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/e\/1FAIpQLSfLWDrkw2utHIdMkpVVHkKZOvfGQpxee_7hs5tAWGLJBud4rA\/viewform\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Commitment Letter<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The day before the admissions appointment, usually on a Thursday, the proctor will receive the test instructions and the Google Hangout link so the student applicants and parents can join the online admissions interviews.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Applicant students and parents will participate in different interviews\/observations led by our specialists. Each interview lasts approximately 30 minutes. Each student will have three interviews, and parents will have one. These are usually held on Fridays between 8:30 a.m. and 12:00 midday (Colombian time)<\/span><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c736a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"1c736a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-36095f6 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"36095f6\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-dc37729 animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"dc37729\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa1ebb7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"aa1ebb7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-27f2d1c parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"27f2d1c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2><strong>The tests<\/strong><\/h2><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Year 3 to Year 13 students<\/span><b>\u00a0<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The applicant student must complete the test at a time convenient for the family within 3-4 days. Please be aware that the tests have an expiration date.\u00a0<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.idat.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">iDAT<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> test. Please provide a quiet place where the student can take the test without interruptions and with no help. An additional device (iPad, tablet, or cellphone) is required to record the student during the test. The student should have a sheet of paper, a pencil, and a calculator.\u00a0 <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The test takes one hour and a half. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The proctor should read the following instructions before conducting the iDAT test: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/student.idat.org\/idat\/starttestno\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IDAT Secure 360 &#8211; Setup steps<\/span><\/a> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and<\/span> <a href=\"https:\/\/student.idat.org\/handbook\/221004_IDAT%20Concise%20handbook_ENG.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Test Taker Handbook<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Writing Test will be sent as an attachment. Once the task has been completed, the proctor must scan it and send it back to<\/span> <a href=\"mailto:reception@cgb.edu.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reception@cgb.edu.co<\/span><\/a><\/li><\/ul><h2><strong>Preschool Students<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Students applying for preschool (Nursery, Reception, Year 1, and Year 2) will receive some worksheets sent by the school, which must be printed by the examiner in advance. The exercises or tests must be completed online together with our specialists, and <\/span><b>not<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> before. Once the test is completed, all sheets must be scanned and sent to <a href=\"mailto:reception@cgb.edu.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reception@cgb.edu.co<\/a> as soon as possible.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Students applying for Nursery or Reception (ages 3 and 4) must also have scissors, paper, the child&#8217;s favourite toy and book, and possibly a collection of small toys.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c3b7c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"6c3b7c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-45e03e1 animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"45e03e1\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4370b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"d4370b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1fc5924 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"1fc5924\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-33961ec animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"33961ec\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f425fdb elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"f425fdb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-35f0bfe animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"35f0bfe\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15f4d1f parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"15f4d1f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Admissions Committee meets every Wednesday to review the applications. If the paperwork is incomplete, the committee will review it the following week.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once the school grants acceptance, we will email the instructions for matriculation, and parents must complete the enrollment process within two weeks.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Children may start school three days after matriculation has taken place, i.e. payments have been made, and contracts have been duly signed and submitted to the school\u2019s office.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contact Daniela, our admissions assistant, at <\/span><a href=\"mailto:reception@cgb.edu.co\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reception@cgb.edu.co<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> if you have any questions.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thank you for your interest and trust in our institution.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kind regards,<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Fiorella Rocha<br \/><em>Admissions Colegio Gran Breta\u00f1a<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\t